This video is amazing! I love how you explain everything so easy,

But, as a person who has studied art and color theory for years now I can say you forgot 2 huge things:
1- the finishes in the jewerly such as gold, silver, rose gold, etc. Do have a huge impact on your undertones

2- The shades such as white, gray and black have also undertones. You can easly find this shades with blue, red, yellow, green undertones same as everycolor. So be aware of that too
